  "name": "Mage Slayer",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Requires MidiQOL, DAE. Make sure to Enable Mage Slayer in the module settings.</em></p>",
      "chat": "When a creature within 5 ft. of you casts a spell, you can use your reaction to make a melee weapon attack against that creature, and when you damage a creature that is concentrating on a spell, that creature has disadvantage on the saving throw it makes to maintain its concentration. You also have advantage on saving throws against spells cast by creatures within 5 ft. of you."
